cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.CE, cs.HC, cs.DB 

This paper uses machine learning methods to analyze public health data and identify diabetic patients at high risk of readmission. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.CY (Computational Biology and Bioinformatics) as the paper deals with healthcare data, cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) as the paper involves cost analysis, cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) as the paper discusses improving healthcare quality, and cs.DB (Databases) as the paper involves analyzing large amounts of healthcare data.
